metadata.name: Noun Cow sk8r inspired by Grant Riven Yun #1/100
metadata.description:
The latest addition to the [MEME sk8r](https://opensea.io/collection/p2memes?search[stringTraits][0][name]=Action&search[stringTraits][0][values][0]=Sk8&search[sortAscending]=true&search[sortBy]=UNIT_PRICE) crew is "Noun Cow sk8r inspired by [Grant Riven Yun](https://www.ribbonriven.com/)"  
When early art was shown to Grant, he replied "DAMN!!!!" (Yes, that is indeed 4 exclamation points)  
DYOR, WAGMI
